isContinued

public static boolean isContinued()
Determines if the document is currently in the state of a "continuing" section (member documentation). If this is the case when the end of a page is reached, the footer of that page will get an additional remark ("continued on the next page") and the header of the next page another one ("continued from last page").

Returns:
true if currently something is continued.
